# CICT Grade Portal — IRJICT Design Sync

Restyle the Flask grade portal to be visually identical to the IRJICT website (https://irjict.isufstcict.com). The portal already uses the right stack (Tailwind 4, HTMX, Inter/JetBrains Mono fonts) but needs color tokens, glassmorphism effects, particle overlays, and button styles corrected to match the IRJICT source exactly.

## Key Differences Found

| Element | Portal (current) | IRJICT (target) |
|---|---|---|
| Primary Maroon | `#5B0000` | `#800000` |
| Accent Gold | `#EAB308` | `#D4AF37` |
| Navbar glass | White topbar | `bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md` |
| Login hero | Pure gradient | Gradient + grid overlay + network dots |
| Button shadow | Yellow | `rgba(212,175,55,1)` gold shadow |
| Paper card | `border border-slate-200` | `border-l-4 border-l-maroon hover:border-l-gold` |
| `--maroon` CSS var | Not defined | `#800000` via `:root` |

---

## Proposed Changes

### CSS / Design Tokens

#### [MODIFY] [input.css](file:///c:/dev/Flask/cict-grade-portal/app/static/css/input.css)

- Sync color tokens: `#5B0000` → `#800000` for primary maroon, `#EAB308` → `#D4AF37` for accent gold
- Add `:root` CSS variables `--maroon` and `--gold` to match IRJICT `globals.css`
- Update glassmorphism nav class `.navbar-glass`
- Add `.paper-card` component (border-l maroon/gold accent)
- Update `.btn-primary` gold shadow to use `D4AF37`
- Add `.skeleton-pulse` and `.badge-*` classes from IRJICT

---

### Templates

#### [MODIFY] [login.html](file:///c:/dev/Flask/cict-grade-portal/templates/auth/login.html)

- Update gradient from `#5B0000` → `#800000` throughout
- Add animated particle/network SVG dot overlay (matches IRJICT hero)
- Update gold orb from `#EAB308` → `#D4AF37`
- Update button shadow to `D4AF37`
- Add CICT logo (use `img` from irjict public URL or static)
- Improve card glassmorphism to match IRJICT more closely

#### [MODIFY] [student/layout.html](file:///c:/dev/Flask/cict-grade-portal/templates/student/layout.html)

- Sidebar: replace `#5B0000` with `#800000` in brand square, avatar border, gold accents
- Active nav link: use `border-l-gold` with `#D4AF37`
- Top bar: switch to glassmorphism `bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-gray-200` (IRJICT `.navbar-glass`)
- Gold avatar ring: use `#D4AF37`

#### [MODIFY] [partials/dashboard.html](file:///c:/dev/Flask/cict-grade-portal/templates/partials/dashboard.html)

- Hero card gradient: update maroon stops to `#800000`
- GWA badge ring: `#D4AF37` border
- Quick stat cards: add `paper-card` left-accent variant
- "View all" link: use `#800000` color
- Add IRJICT-style subtle network/dot background to hero card

#### [MODIFY] [partials/grades.html](file:///c:/dev/Flask/cict-grade-portal/templates/partials/grades.html)

- Semester switcher active: `bg-[#800000]`
- GWA banner: adjust border to `#800000/20`
- Table header bar: `bg-[#800000]`
- Subject code color: `#800000`
- Footer tfoot: `border-[#800000]/20` and `bg-[#800000]/5`

#### [MODIFY] [partials/profile.html](file:///c:/dev/Flask/cict-grade-portal/templates/partials/profile.html)

- Profile banner gradient: `#800000`
- Avatar bg: `#1A1A1A` with `border-white` (keep)
- Role badge: use `#800000/10` and `text-[#800000]`
- Section value color: `#800000`
- Use `paper-card` class on info cards

