## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification (Browser Tool)
After applying changes, I will use the browser subagent to:
1. Start the Flask dev server (`flask run`)
2. Navigate to `http://127.0.0.1:5000/auth/login` — verify login page matches IRJICT aesthetic (maroon radial gradient, gold orb, network overlay, glassmorphism card)
3. Navigate to `http://127.0.0.1:5000/student/dashboard` — verify sidebar maroon, gold active state, glassmorphism topbar, hero card gradient
4. Navigate to `http://127.0.0.1:5000/student/grades` — verify ledger table header in `#800000`, gold GWA display
5. Take screenshots and embed in walkthrough

> [!NOTE]
> No automated test suite exists for the frontend. Verification is entirely visual via browser screenshots.
